If you have more questions about USTs, you can get in touch with the Site Assessment and Support Unit (SASU) at DEEP at this email: DEEP.Leakingust@ct.gov

Two ARPA related resources that include information on some municipal projects are: 
American Rescue Plan Project Inventory (https://data.ct.gov/Government/American-Rescue-Plan-Project-Inventory/rcur-2uns/about_data);
American Rescue Plan Act (ARPA) Funding & Project Inventory Dashboard (https://data.ct.gov/stories/s/d8eu-4zpa)

This information is available in the National Archives. I will link to a few resources below that may help address your question:
WWII Casualty Lists guidance - document from the National Archive explaining how to find information on WWII casualties (https://gcc02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.archives.gov%2Ffiles%2Fresearch%2Fmilitary%2Fww2%2Fcasualty-lists.pdf&data=05%7C02%7Cpauline.zaldonis%40ct.gov%7C806e89f3260b4bd98d4a08dcf81d3596%7C118b7cfaa3dd48b9b02631ff69bb738b%7C0%7C0%7C638658051584506656%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&sdata=Ng3ERDSfoSdVyTPUlKicOc4szvXSlIKO0CCOxRJDMWY%3D&reserved=0);
National Archives Catalog - online resource for accessing information in the National Archives (https://gcc02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcatalog.archives.gov%2F&data=05%7C02%7Cpauline.zaldonis%40ct.gov%7C806e89f3260b4bd98d4a08dcf81d3596%7C118b7cfaa3dd48b9b02631ff69bb738b%7C0%7C0%7C638658051584548502%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&sdata=6DcefYNl88QkOy38pOVDY95LG1oXLwToW567YutDaew%3D&reserved=0);
National Archives WWII Records page - more information about WWII records in the National Archives (https://gcc02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.archives.gov%2Fresearch%2Fmilitary%2Fww2&data=05%7C02%7Cpauline.zaldonis%40ct.gov%7C806e89f3260b4bd98d4a08dcf81d3596%7C118b7cfaa3dd48b9b02631ff69bb738b%7C0%7C0%7C638658051584564127%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&sdata=k8N1HBsAP2DFT2s%2F1Ngm2%2FDE3u52Xchhvx6knEToN1M%3D&reserved=0)
